column5: so nothing going on, you feel like just kicking back and watching the boob tube so here are the choices  Harry Potter marathon  The Walking Dead marathon  Breaking Bad marathon  Modern Family marathon or The Simpsons marathon      as I type I am watching   The Walking Dead marathon  which would you watch...
Breaking Bad.
Lol!,  I alternated between Average Joe's the underdog story and HP the prisoner of askaban.  But I am tired of the Simpsons, and never got I to modern family. I also don't get the other two...
Terry,watch walking dead till the new season starts at 9pm. It'll get you back up to snuff lol.I'll be watching the laffs till then.Looks like a good season starting for the walking Dead.
BAZINGA
breaking bad any day

Terry,watch walking dead till the new season starts at 9pm. It'll get you back up to snuff lol.I'll be watching the laffs till then.Looks like a good season starting for the walking Dead. yup a refresher leading up to the season opener   Bri, big bang wasn't on the list.....lol
It's Thanksgiving and it's Sunday, watch football!
Bri, big bang wasn't on the list.....lol
yup im also watching the walking dead marathon, leading up to the new season
Watching Terry and Brian's videos of fishing.
With those as the choices? The DVD player would get a workout.

I would just watch any of the series that I haven't seen that magically have appeared on a harddrive I have. I am doing that right now. Wonders of the Monsoon.  I gave up satellite last month because I got sick of paying for so many duplicates of the EXACT same programming. The give you 180 channels but only 15 different shows, at a time, you would even consider, 10 of which are reruns. Great scam for the providers though.  Out of the choices listed though? It is close but Breaking Bad over Walking Dead by the brim of Heisenberg's hat at the finish line.
New season of trailer park boys in Netflix . Fantastic entertainment, especially with the tiny amount of tv I watch nowadays
not one of the choices..........but if ur into demented comedy, an "its always sunny in philadelphia" marathon is where its at. That show pretty much  runs on a loop in my home if the tv is on
I agree with It's always sunny in Philadelphia is a great show. One of my favourites. That and Trailer Park Boys... I could watch a marathon of either, any day.
Tonight for me is catching up on episodes #4 and #5 SOA,what a nice show .LOL
Orange is the new black..... Best show I have seen in a long time. But out of the shows you listed... I would choose breaking bad.  G
Tonight for me is catching up on episodes #4 and #5 SOA,what a nice show .LOL  SOA is wrapping up a lot of loose ends quickly this season.
SOA is wrapping up a lot of loose ends quickly this season. Just finished episode 5,WOW is all I can say!!!!!!!!!!!
Dang there's so much good stuff on TV... but we end up here watching episodes of OFC pretty well everyday. lol.
